narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I think this course is very well taught.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, especially if you are looking to fulfill the lessons for credit requirement. Although finding the motivation to get out bed and sing whole tone scales at 9:30 in the morning can be difficult, the classroom environment is laid-back and friendly and you'll learn and develop some useful skills along the way. The required weekly keyboard labs can be fun if you go in with a good partner, especially since you'll be able to decide what kind of material/skills you want to work on for the semester.
Yes, it provides a fairly useful base on which to build.
